Essential packages to install: base base-devel linux linux-firmware linux-headers intel-ucode
Grub installation: grub-install --target=i386-pc /dev/<partition>
		   grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg

If this error message shows up after completing installation and booting: 

"<root_partition> mounted successfully but /sbin/init doesn't exist
Bailing out...", download "systemd-sysvcompat" package.


